e for me, I know it's you."],[2686,2790,"You're, genuinely"],[2790,2982,"there's no one else in here for me."],[2982,3207,"So if you really are like that, unsure"],[3207,3319,"after, like, spending"],[3319,3445,"this much time together"],[3445,3687,"that's not the space that I'm in."],[3687,3762,"I don't want to"],[3762,3862,"explore anyone else."],[3862,3999,"Like, for me, it's you."],[3999,4054,"Symantha."],[4054,4229,"I actually do have a connection"],[4229,4300,"with this girl."],[4300,4441,"Whether you like it or not."],[4441,4642,"You went and had your fun."],[4642,4821,"Now, the second I get to go do it,"],[4821,4913,"I'm not allowed?"],[4913,5113,"Like, the double standard is crazy."],[5113,5242,"I definitely came here"],[5242,5326,"looking for love"],[5326,5430,"and to find my soulmate."],[5463,5618,"But I did come in"],[5618,5818,"days after everybody else."],[5847,6060,"And it does cause chaos,"],[6060,6110,"even though that's"],[6110,6264,"that's not what I was trying to do."],[6268,6377,"So we're here to see"],[6377,6569,"who our soulmates are."],[6602,6823,"I kind of want to see what happens"],[6823,6927,"at elimination tonight."],[6940,7036,"I'm still partnered up"],[7036,7194,"with her, obviously."],[7194,7286,"So are you telling me"],[7286,7374,"you still don't know"],[7474,7532,"who your like"],[7532,7657,"choice is?"],[7657,7836,"I do think Cru is my soulmate."],[7891,8120,"I've done my exploring."],[8120,8433,"And now I need Cru to make his choice."],[8454,8616,"You don't need to pick me, but I."],[8616,8800,"Yeah, I want an answer."],[8800,8933,"No, no, no, what I'm asking is"],[8933,9021,"it's an ultimatum."],[9021,9159,"If I don't tell you right now"],[9159,9267,"that I want you, you're saying"],[9267,9321,"you're done with me."],[9351,9455,"I'm not trying to give you"],[9455,9526,"an ultimatum."],[9526,9626,"I don't want to say like"],[9626,9684,"we're over."],[9684,9934,"I don't want I do not want to say that."],[9934,10126,"I'm being so honest with you."],[10126,10251,"Ultimatums."],[10256,10314,"I hate them."],[10314,10447,"You're putting your partner"],[10447,10523,"into a corner"],[10523,10652,"and making them choose"],[10652,10773,"when they're not ready."],[10773,10885,"I need to have another"],[10885,11073,"conversation with Symmy,"],[11094,11390,"and then I can give you an answer."],[11390,11490,"I have a couple questions"],[11490,11557,"to ask her."],[11557,11761,"This is our last conversation, Cru."],[11761,11999,"like we don't have the time."],[12099,12212,"We literally have to go"],[12212,12345,"to the elimination."],[12345,12487,"Symantha and Julie,"],[12487,12654,"which one are you going to pick?"],[12708,12850,"Cru wants me to wait"],[12850,13004,"for him to talk to Sym."],[13004,13217,"What kind of bullshit is that?"]],"75":[[0,196,"Cru and I just had a tough conversation,"],[196,437,"and now I have no idea"],[437,567,"what he's going to do."],[608,754,"We both hurt each other."],[754,884,"We both were petty."],[884,967,"We both did that."],[967,1088,"So now where do we go?"],[1088,1213,"I just feel like"],[1213,1388,"he doesn't want me anymore."],[1451,1514,"What just happened?"],[1514,1814,"So, like, we had our talk"],[1826,1872,"He's like"],[1872,1951,"you're giving me an ultimatum."],[1951,2002,"That's not fair."],[2002,2114,"And I was like, no,"],[2114,2310,"it's because I know myself"],[2310,2494,"and like I cannot sit with you"],[2494,2610,"at the end of this,"],[2652,2777,"knowing that you couldn't"],[2777,2915,"pick me right now"],[2915,3148,"and then pick you and be your default"],[3161,3286,"like, if you don't know,"],[3286,3486,"like, I can't do that."],[3486,3586,"Right now,"],[3616,3724,"Cru is it for me."],[3724,3983,"And it sucks that he doesn't know if I'm"],[3983,4058,"it for him."],[4058,4216,"It sucks seeing him with"],[4216,4300,"another connection."],[4300,4466,"It sucks seeing that they"],[4466,4625,"definitely have chemistry."],[4625,4733,"Fuck him."],[4733,4967,"I'm sorry, but that that's just what it is"],[4967,5030,"because you're not going to sit there"],[5030,5080,"and be like"],[5080,5242,"I'm going to decide after elimination."],[5242,5313,"What?"],[5313,5409,"It makes no sense."],[5409,5563,"He's like, I want to see what happens."],[5563,5622,"Why?"],[5622,5772,"See what happens?"],[5772,5901,"I want to see what happens?"],[5901,6001,"He's like, you're giving me"],[6001,6072,"an ultimatum."],[6072,6181,"I'm like I'm not."],[6181,6335,"But I know myself."],[6335,6439,"And, like, I'm not going"],[6439,6519,"to let myself"],[6519,6673,"be your default."],[6735,6890,"Julie is my girl."],[6890,7002,"So we're going to need"],[7002,7090,"to do something to make"],[7090,7190,"things right."],[7278,7411,"So what do you think he's,"],[7411,7486,"do we vote Cru out?"],[7486,7645,"Just stick to the plan."],[7645,7799,"Sym did say to"],[7799,7937,"some of the girls last night"],[7937,8049,"that she feels like"],[8049,8208,"her type isn't in the house."],[8208,8337,"Her type is"],[8337,8508,"tall, dark, and handsome."],[8516,8671,"So the plan is,"],[8671,8846,"I'm going to vote with my girls"],[8846,8963,"and we're going to vote"],[8963,9046,"out Sym."],[9046,9225,"Because I want to see his face"],[9225,9396,"when it's like, I gave you"],[9396,9471,"a fucking chance"],[9471,9530,"to choose me"],[9530,9822,"And you didn't. You didn't."],[9822,9918,"So number one,"],[9918,10122,"we need to wipe these tears."],[10210,10281,"Number two,"],[10281,10468,"you need to get ready and look like"],[10468,10527,"a bad bitch."],[10552,10777,"Pop the fuck off."],[10777,10877,"And you need to get."],[10877,10985,"We need to turn up"],[10985,11094,"our turn up music and"],[11094,11219,"remember who the fuck"],[11219,11453,"Julie is, okay? Okay."],[11453,11524,"I love you girls."],[11524,11657,"Thank you so much."],[11770,12037,"I love you guys."],[12037,12208,"I also care about Cru."],[12208,12274,"So if that's like,"],[12274,12420,"if that's his actual match,"],[12420,12554,"then I want him to be happy too."],[12587,12887,"And then maybe mine's just not here."],[12992,13259,"I'm really hurt."],[13259,13421,"At least you have us."],[13421,13551,"I know."]],"76":[[4,108,"Are you and Sav"],[108,179,"really feeling each other?"],[179,221,"Yeah."],[221,304,"I'm going to keep talking to her"],[304,362,"after this,"],[362,475,"no matter what."],[475,538,"Really?"],[538,633,"Truly."],[633,742,"Like, all my life."],[742,909,"She's the only girl I followed here."],[909,1005,"Only one I followed this morning,"],[1005,1067,"to be honest with you."],[1067,1188,"You think the feeling is mutual?"],[1188,1255,"Yeah."],[1255,1338,"I did a lot of thinking"],[1338,1409,"and the things that we"],[1409,1463,"had in common."],[1463,1609,"And I think we get along very well."],[1609,1751,"I believe that"],[1751,1893,"Savannah is my soulmate."],[1893,2014,"I don't want to throw"],[2014,2093,"anyone under the bus,"],[2093,2193,"but like,"],[2202,2565,"I question whether your connection"],[2565,2669,"with Sav is as"],[2669,2831,"genuine as you think it is."],[2857,2915,"Fair."],[2915,3053,"And I'll tell you why."],[3053,3224,"Because yesterday I was with her."],[3224,3407,"So we were talking about it."],[3470,3570,"When you walked up,"],[3570,3762,"she very blatantly expressed"],[3762,3916,"that she did not find you attractive."],[3916,4049,"Fair."],[4049,4129,"Yeah, and she said that"],[4129,4191,"in her interview too."],[4191,4404,"Fair but girls don't care about looks."],[4404,4500,"They care about emotion."],[4500,4567,"And I think that's why"],[4567,4692,"she quickly switched to me."],[4692,4808,"I mean I think looks have a little bit"],[4808,4942,"to do with it, but you're right."],[4942,5059,"Maybe you charmed her up."],[5059,5201,"Like, I don't know."],[5201,5292,"But I also think"],[5292,5392,"she might be trying to save face"],[5392,5476,"because she was worried"],[5476,5626,"that she would get voted out tonight."],[5626,5747,"Because she didn't have, like,"],[5747,5843,"a great match up."],[5843,5905,"Yeah."],[5905,6006,"I didn't think that she"],[6006,6060,"was worried at all."],[6060,6172,"Even when I heard the girls talking,"],[6172,6260,"like the other ones that were"],[6260,6322,"worried about getting"],[6322,6489,"voted out, Sav doesn't feel."],[6552,6731,"That's why it's also like when I told the"],[6731,6806,"girls like hey."],[6806,6906,"They're all voting me out."],[6906,7052,"They're like, why?"],[7052,7186,"I feel like I just"],[7186,7311,"finally got my chance."],[7311,7353,"Yeah."],[7353,7453,"She told me she didn't have"],[7453,7603,"a connection with you."],[7603,7695,"No, it's more of, like,"],[7695,7836,"a platonic thing, but."],[7836,7916,"Yeah."],[7916,8249,"But yeah, I'm just telling you, like what"],[8249,8391,"she told me yesterday."],[8416,8608,"If it's me or Ty, I'm going to try to turn"],[8608,8717,"people against him."],[8721,8800,"No shade."],[8800,8888,"I just don't want to go home."]],"77":[[221,367,"Tonight's the night."],[367,483,"They're getting rid of someone,"],[483,696,"and my head's on the chopping block."],[696,909,"And even if my soulmate isn't here,"],[909,996,"I want to stay"],[996,1197,"because I'm having a great time."],[1197,1284,"I want to know what's"],[1284,1409,"really going on."],[1443,1651,"And I thought I talked to you."],[1651,1793,"You do realize if Ty goes home,"],[1793,1914,"I'm leaving with him."],[1914,1989,"Who else am I going to"],[1989,2043,"connect with, Toni?"],[2043,2147,"We've already tried it out."],[2218,2310,"You literally told me"],[2310,2427,"you have a girl back home."],[2427,2502,"That's not true."],[2502,2615,"I don't have a girl back home."],[2615,2660,"You told that to a"],[2660,2731,"bunch of different people."],[2731,2811,"No, there's a girl"],[2811,2927,"I'm interested in back home."],[2927,3007,"That doesn't mean I have"],[3007,3094,"a girl back home."],[3094,3190,"It's not like that."],[3190,3453,"So there is a girl I like back at home."],[3453,3536,"All right."],[3536,3774,"That came out, that came out earlier."],[3774,3899,"I thought maybe I'd meet"],[3899,3949,"someone with a better"],[3949,4012,"connection here,"],[4012,4162,"but it's very clear to me."],[4162,4341,"Like I don't feel a connection like that"],[4341,4462,"with anyone!"],[4462,4625,"But I am having fun."],[4767,4992,"Where are you at with Ty?"],[4992,5159,"Do you like him?"],[5159,5246,"I do like him."],[5246,5338,"He's the first guy that I've"],[5338,5472,"actually connected with."],[5472,5593,"I'm voting for him."],[5593,5784,"I'm voting for him, and I'm"],[5784,5885,"Then I'm leaving tonight."],[5885,6014,"So it was nice knowing you all,"],[6014,6110,"because I'm actually here to"],[6110,6168,"find my soulmate,"],[6168,6356,"and Toni, I'm sorry. It is not you."],[6356,6448,"I mean, I agree."],[6448,6573,"I think you're cool, but like"],[6573,6740,"So then who do you,"],[6740,6915,"Brynn, nobody else thinks that you're"],[6915,6998,"their soulmate either."],[6998,7203,"I think I can find it."],[7203,7503,"I hope you have fun, but yeah, I'm"],[7503,7574,"leaving tonight."],[7574,7770,"So if you all send Ty home,"],[7770,7895,"I'm gone too."],[7895,8095,"So majority of the other roommates"],[8095,8266,"don't think that Ty was genuine"],[8266,8337,"with me and that"],[8337,8450,"our connection isn't real,"],[8470,8721,"but just because I had bad luck at the"],[8721,8817,"beginning of this"],[8833,8938,"doesn't mean that my"],[8938,9063,"short lived connection"],[9063,9209,"isn't just as real."],[9213,9330,"I know it's real."],[9330,9555,"I just hate that a little bit of them"],[9555,9642,"aren't believing it."],[9768,9897,"I just don't understand"],[9897,10047,"why the one time that I actually"],[10047,10110,"find somebody"],[10135,10301,"that I'm decently interested in and"],[10301,10472,"actually excited to like explore"],[10497,10648,"everyone's going on a smear campaign"],[10648,10735,"to send him home,"],[10735,10827,"when he's the only one"],[10827,10935,"that's actually chose me"],[10935,11011,"or like, showed any"],[11011,11127,"interest in me."],[11144,11298,"Right now, he's the only one here"],[11298,11444,"that matches my freak."],[11448,11565,"And if they send him home,"],[11565,11661,"I'm leaving too."]],"78":[[362,379,"All right,"],[379,571,"so with elimination, tonight's kind of"],[571,738,"just had me thinking a little bit."],[742,838,"Now we've gotten to"],[838,930,"know each other"],[930,1080,"a little bit better after today."],[1080,1180,"Connect a little."],[1180,1297,"How do you feel things"],[1297,1430,"might progress with us?"],[1447,1468,"You know,"],[1468,1643,"you think there's a possible chance of"],[1705,1780,"you know, a relationship"],[1780,1901,"outside of the show?"],[1947,2060,"I think it says a lot"],[2060,2185,"like how close that we've gotten"],[2185,2318,"in such a short amount of time."],[2318,2452,"Obviously, like we have"],[2452,2540,"a very close"],[2540,2615,"physical connection."],[2615,2756,"We feel very safe around each other."],[2765,2923,"Those are things that I look for,"],[2957,3048,"you know, in a person."],[3048,3294,"And so I think I'd definitely be open"],[3294,3432,"to talking more about that"],[3432,3695,"and kind of seeing how tonight goes"],[3695,3870,"and how we're both feeling about things."],[3908,3991,"You never know"],[3991,4191,"what could happen, especially here."],[4346,4475,"So there's no guarantee that"],[4475,4667,"one of us or either of us are here,"],[4675,4796,"you know, tomorrow morning."],[4900,5067,"So if you'd like,"],[5105,5251,"maybe we could just"],[5251,5401,"try a little kiss"],[5401,5522,"on our own?"],[5522,5597,"Yeah."],[5605,5676,"See how it is?"],[5676,5739,"Yeah?"],[5739,5789,"Yeah."],[5789,5997,"Maybe call it a new yoga position?"],[6147,6268,"Sure."],[6272,6343,"Just in case."],[6343,6464,"I mean, this could be"],[6564,6698,"this could be the last time,"],[6698,6819,"you know, that?"],[7240,7378,"Brynn, you and me."],[7390,7570,"I'm closing the door on everyone else."],[7603,7745,"I just want to pursue you."],[7782,7949,"And if it works out, that's great."],[7949,8133,"If it doesn't, then at least I'll know"],[8133,8308,"I gave you my full energy,"],[8308,8429,"attention and focus."],[8554,8604,"Promise you're not going to"],[8604,8675,"vote me home?"],[8779,8917,"As long as you don't vote me."],[8917,9038,"Got a deal."],[9209,9271,"I definitely think"],[9271,9392,"we're each other's secret soulmates."],[9459,9588,"Now we just need to"],[9588,9709,"make it through elimination."]],"79":[[513,633,"Elimination night."],[633,834,"Someone's going home."],[846,984,"I'm feeling pretty confident"],[984,1172,"that I'm not the one going home."],[1172,1376,"Me and Cru kind of hit it off,"],[1376,1618,"and I really am here to find my soulmate."],[1622,1747,"I think I'm going to stay."],[1747,1910,"If my girls don't pull through"],[1910,2068,"and vote Sym off,"],[2068,2189,"I could lose Cru."],[2189,2335,"I'm really nervous"],[2335,2444,"because I know for a fact"],[2444,2494,"the girls would"],[2494,2644,"probably vote for Sym,"],[2669,2765,"but I'm just scared that"],[2765,2831,"if that's the case,"],[2831,2940,"the guys would also vote"],[2940,3036,"for the guy that I like,"],[3040,3136,"Ty to go home."],[3136,3290,"Two people are going home tonight"],[3290,3449,"and I refuse to let it be me."],[3449,3570,"I'm going to stay here"],[3570,3674,"and find my soulmate"],[3691,3799,"with Ty."],[3799,3945,"I don't feel confident at all."],[3945,4099,"Apparently my soulmate's here."],[4099,4320,"But I have no idea who it is."],[4325,4412,"No clue."],[4412,4537,"I just don't want to go home."],[4537,4625,"I have so much"],[4625,4738,"unfinished business here"],[4742,4846,"I'm not ready to leave."],[5084,5188,"My singles."],[5188,5301,"The time has come"],[5301,5455,"for you to eliminate one guy"],[5501,5689,"and one girl."],[5689,5764,"For some of you,"],[5764,5926,"this elimination could give you"],[5926,6035,"the freedom to pursue"],[6035,6110,"other connections."],[6110,6331,"But for two unlucky singles,"],[6331,6435,"your soulmate search"],[6435,6531,"ends tonight."],[6744,6852,"One by one,"],[6852,6952,"each of you will"],[6952,7061,"walk up to the gazebo"],[7082,7269,"and place a flower in the vase"],[7269,7540,"of the girl and guy who you think"],[7549,7674,"are the least committed"],[7674,7757,"to finding love."],[7828,7928,"The boy and girl"],[7928,8020,"with the highest votes"],[8020,8283,"will be eliminated without knowing"],[8283,8395,"their soulmate."],[8395,8512,"And remember,"],[8512,8621,"at the end of the week,"],[8654,8792,"you are to pick the person"],[8792,8850,"you believe to be"],[8850,8967,"your soulmate."],[8967,9121,"If you guess correctly,"],[9121,9321,"you win love and money."],[9376,9505,"But if your soulmate"],[9505,9705,"gets sent home tonight,"],[9722,9930,"no love and no prize money"],[9930,10035,"for you."],[10035,10126,"Choose wisely."],[10523,10652,"Julie, you will"],[10652,10852,"cast the first votes."],[11353,11557,"We're supposed to vote for who"],[11557,11853,"we don't think is here for love."],[11974,12157,"I'm voting for Symantha."]],"80":[[120,304,"I don't think she's here to"],[304,504,"genuinely find love."],[613,775,"This one's tough"],[775,1005,"because I consider"],[1005,1163,"this person a friend."],[1163,1322,"But at the end of the day,"],[1322,1397,"I want Savannah"],[1397,1651,"to be able to find a genuine connection."],[1651,1885,"And I think she has that with Ty"],[1885,2060,"and I want her to be able to explore it."],[2060,2260,"So I'm going in for Toni."],[2431,2544,"Savannah didn't have"],[2544,2690,"a strong connection at first,"],[2690,2790,"but now her and Ty are"],[2790,2927,"hitting it off, and I want her to be able"],[2927,3069,"to explore that connection."],[3069,3182,"I'm sorry, Toni,"],[3182,3319,"you're my friend, but"],[3361,3561,"Savannah is my girl."],[3641,3716,"Cru."],[3716,3912,"You're next."],[4250,4421,"Okay,"],[4421,4550,"the reason why"],[4550,4679,"I'm voting for this person."],[4725,4838,"I literally am switching"],[4838,4904,"it on the spot"],[4904,4963,"right now."]],"81":[[271,321,"The reason"],[321,529,"why I'm voting for this person,"],[546,725,"because I think she is"],[725,821,"too closed off."],[834,1113,"I think she's not open to love."],[1117,1305,"I think she's just kind of here."],[1305,1505,"And it was going to be"],[1564,1755,"Savannah, but I think her and Ty"],[1755,1893,"actually have something,"],[1893,2010,"so I'm going to switch it"],[2010,2093,"to Brynn."],[2623,2761,"This is a tough one."],[2761,2932,"This is a tough one."],[2932,3128,"I am voting for this guy to go home,"],[3128,3286,"because I don't think"],[3286,3324,"he has"],[3324,3436,"any good connections"],[3436,3557,"with the girls in the house."],[3649,3741,"It just sucks."],[3741,3937,"I just voted to send Brynn home,"],[3937,4070,"and now I have to stab one"],[4070,4270,"of my boys in the back too."],[4312,4512,"I hate it."],[4788,4884,"This is going to be"],[4884,5084,"a very tough decision"],[5084,5163,"for me tonight."],[5188,5313,"It's been kind of confusing"],[5313,5359,"to figure out,"],[5359,5392,"you know,"],[5392,5543,"who's here for the right reasons"],[5543,5605,"and who isn't."],[5714,5847,"For the girls,"],[5847,6064,"tonight I am going to pick."],[6748,6948,"For the guys."],[6965,7190,"Tonight I am going to pick Ty."]],"82":[[154,396,"I chose Ty, and I do really stand by that."],[400,492,"As much as I don't want"],[492,558,"to hurt the girls"],[558,700,"or feel like I'm letting them down,"],[729,884,"but the choice was made."],[884,938,"Whether or not"],[942,1038,"it was right or wrong,"],[1038,1176,"I don't know."],[1176,1376,"Ty, cast your votes now."],[1447,1589,"For my first vote."],[1589,1701,"I'm voting for this person"],[1701,1847,"because I really"],[1847,2047,"don't think they're here for love."],[2077,2273,"The person is Toni."],[2489,2644,"Now, for the second person,"],[2644,2706,"the reason I'm"],[2706,2861,"voting them out is because"],[2886,3061,"out of all the talks I've had with them,"],[3061,3178,"it feels like"],[3178,3269,"the least amount of love"],[3269,3370,"coming from them."],[3370,3490,"The person I'm voting for"],[3549,3720,"is Brynn."]],"83":[[20,125,"Symantha."],[125,325,"It's your turn."],[688,838,"I voted for Savannah"],[838,1063,"because I don't think that she's here"],[1063,1242,"to find her secret soulmate."],[1242,1443,"I don't think she's vibed with anybody."],[1455,1576,"We're looking for people"],[1576,1730,"who want to find"],[1730,1839,"their soulmate here."],[1839,1960,"Ty and Savannah?"],[2002,2089,"I don't know."],[2089,2223,"Maybe they're soulmates."],[2223,2302,"Maybe they're not."],[2302,2369,"I almost feel like"],[2369,2477,"they just chose each other"],[2477,2590,"because Savannah didn't"],[2590,2790,"find love with anybody else."],[3123,3219,"Josiah."],[3219,3420,"Vote now."],[3486,3682,"I choose this person because I feel like"],[3682,3883,"they're here to just stir up drama."],[3937,4137,"This person is Ty."],[4341,4437,"Alectra."],[4437,4637,"You're next."],[4683,4884,"Oh my God."],[4892,5092,"I'm picking this person"],[5130,5384,"because I don't think"],[5413,5689,"anyone here is her soulmate."],[5693,5901,"I don't think anyone here is her type."],[5997,6239,"I feel like it was pretty obvious."],[6377,6577,"Symantha."],[6744,6898,"I'm picking this next person"],[7007,7211,"because I feel like"],[7211,7507,"they aren't in it for the right reasons."],[7540,7811,"I'm choosing Toni."],[8712,8846,"Truthfully, I kind of heard"],[8846,8933,"through the grapevine"],[8933,9067,"that while some of us are here"],[9067,9242,"to potentially find their soulmates,"],[9242,9346,"that you were kind of here"],[9346,9547,"to raise a little bit of hell."],[9551,9663,"I'm going to say Ty."]],"84":[[16,108,"For the women."],[108,233,"Earlier today, I kind of heard"],[233,325,"a few tall tales"],[325,442,"being thrown around about"],[442,550,"why I should vote"],[550,650,"this person off."],[650,855,"Turns out none of that was really true."],[871,967,"Kind of rubbed me"],[967,1076,"the wrong way a little bit."],[1497,1584,"Savannah."],[1584,1785,"Vote now."],[1822,1981,"I'm voting for this person"],[1981,2106,"because he just went on"],[2106,2302,"a smear campaign on my name"],[2302,2506,"and on my man's name,"],[2506,2652,"because he's trying to save his ass."],[2652,2756,"He has been coupled up"],[2756,2840,"with every single girl"],[2840,3148,"here and has still not found anybody."],[3178,3390,"So I am going to give this one"],[3390,3474,"to Toni."],[4045,4266,"I kind of feel bad about this one"],[4266,4466,"because I really do like this girl."],[4475,4792,"But I do love my girl Julie, and I really"],[4792,5017,"have to be there for her"],[5017,5246,"and protect the man that she likes."],[5246,5430,"Make sure that they stay together."],[5430,5630,"So as much as I feel"],[5630,5743,"really bad about this,"],[5743,5834,"I'm going to have to give this"],[5834,5914,"one to Symantha."],[6331,6531,"That was hard."],[6652,6781,"Toni."],[6781,6981,"Place your votes."],[6986,7186,"For the guys, I'm voting for Ty."],[7219,7361,"Nothing against you, man, but"],[7361,7486,"to be honest"],[7486,7686,"it's me or you."],[7753,7953,"And for the girls."],[8833,8908,"Singles."],[8908,9038,"The votes are in,"],[9038,9205,"and two of you will immediately"],[9205,9305,"pack your bags"],[9305,9421,"and leave the mansion"],[9442,9663,"without knowing your soulmate."]],"85":[[325,450,"Singles."],[450,571,"The votes are in."],[571,754,"And two of you will immediately"],[754,988,"pack your bags and leave the mansion"],[1076,1276,"without knowing their soulmate."],[1397,1501,"I think people would be"],[1501,1647,"stupid to send me home."],[1659,1856,"I've been the one crying over a boy."],[1856,2014,"I've really put my heart out there."],[2014,2198,"So if people send me home then"],[2198,2544,"they're dumb and wrong."],[2594,2794,"Julie."],[2932,3132,"You are safe."],[3432,3632,"Jace."],[3682,3883,"You are safe."],[4087,4287,"Alectra."],[4362,4562,"You are safe."],[4988,5201,"I think I could be the one going home,"],[5201,5338,"because Julie"],[5338,5476,"could rally the troops"],[5476,5551,"and get me out of here."],[5551,5714,"You just never know in this house."],[5714,5839,"Every time I double down"],[5839,5980,"on something, it screws me."],[5980,6114,"So now I'm kind of scared."],[6114,6314,"I don't know what's going to happen."],[6368,6569,"Cru,"],[6581,6652,"you are safe."],[7061,7261,"Savannah."],[7286,7486,"You are safe."],[7903,8103,"Josiah."],[8187,8387,"You are safe."],[8771,9059,"Brynn, Symantha, Toni, and Ty."],[9100,9442,"Two of you are going home tonight."],[9501,9626,"I don't know what's going to happen."],[9626,9793,"Symantha just got in here."],[9793,9893,"She's clearly here to be open"],[9893,10001,"to find a soulmate."],[10001,10118,"But I'm scared."],[10118,10201,"I have no idea"],[10201,10268,"who's going to go home."],[10268,10343,"As much as, like,"],[10343,10435,"I don't really feel like"],[10435,10618,"Sym is in here for the right reasons,"],[10618,10764,"I also don't want to be"],[10764,11002,"chosen by default either."],[11006,11207,"So maybe she should stay."],[11219,11473,"If my guy Ty goes home,"],[11473,11574,"I'm leaving with him."]],"86":[[358,458,"So I'm standing there"],[458,558,"right next to Ty"],[558,646,"the new guy"],[646,809,"who no one really even knows,"],[809,946,"and Rebecca is there,"],[946,1038,"and she's going to announce"],[1038,1213,"who is exiled."],[1276,1397,"I'm on the chopping block,"],[1397,1543,"which sort of surprises me,"],[1543,1651,"but part of that"],[1651,1747,"could be people questioning"],[1747,1947,"the authenticity of relationships."],[1951,2206,"Part of it could be the girls feeling"],[2206,2335,"I just spend too much time"],[2335,2406,"with the guys."],[2419,2481,"I don't know too much"],[2481,2610,"about how Brynn feels"],[2610,2711,"about her relationship"],[2711,2773,"with the girls."],[2773,2919,"Obviously people have heard"],[2919,2982,"Brynn the bro."],[2982,3069,"Like she gets along"],[3069,3161,"with the guys pretty well"],[3161,3244,"and we kind of all"],[3244,3445,"hung out, especially me, her, and Toni,"],[3461,3549,"but I don't know."],[3549,3624,"That doesn't mean"],[3624,3745,"she should get voted off."],[3745,3895,"My original intention"],[3895,4004,"was to find my soulmate,"],[4004,4304,"but I did disrupt and cause chaos,"],[4304,4400,"even though that's not"],[4400,4525,"what I was trying to do."],[4529,4692,"I came here to find love."],[5176,5376,"Symantha and Brynn."],[5651,5851,"Symantha,"],[5905,6106,"you are eliminated."],[6185,6235,"Which means"],[6235,6468,"Brynn, you are safe."],[6527,6727,"That's okay."],[7123,7286,"I'm going home."],[7286,7407,"I think that people"],[7407,7528,"voted for me because"],[7561,7745,"I came in a few days late."],[7745,7866,"and they were already"],[7866,8008,"coupled up, and"],[8008,8170,"I think that caused distress"],[8170,8266,"and they needed to"],[8266,8375,"remove the obstacle."],[8525,8608,"Sym did say"],[8608,8812,"to some of the girls last night"],[8812,8950,"that she feels like"],[8950,9079,"her type isn't in the house."],[9088,9217,"Her type is"],[9217,9367,"tall, dark, and handsome."],[9367,9601,"So in a way, it might be good"],[9601,9801,"that Sym is going home."],[9805,9968,"Cru got screwed again."],[9968,10126,"Symantha got sent home."],[10126,10272,"She literally just got here."],[10272,10472,"I had a really good connection with her."],[10523,10627,"More so than I did"],[10627,10668,"with Julie"],[10668,10873,"in certain areas, and I really"],[10873,10985,"wanted to explore that."],[10985,11186,"When she walked away"],[11186,11277,"and I was standing there"],[11290,11423,"looking like a freaking idiot"],[11423,11490,"yet again,"],[11519,11720,"I felt like we missed our chance."],[11782,11920,"In all honesty,"],[11920,12049,"I think that Julie and Cru"],[12049,12174,"are both great people"],[12174,12333,"and I hope that they are soulmates"],[12333,12504,"and I hope that they do find it in the end."],[12871,13008,"Toni and Ty."],[13008,13184,"Now it's time for one of you"],[13184,13304,"to be eliminated."]],"87":[[400,533,"They're getting rid of someone,"],[533,671,"and my head's on"],[671,750,"the chopping block."],[767,967,"It's between me and the new guy Ty."],[988,1188,"Someone's going home."],[1601,1801,"Ty and Toni."],[1864,2085,"Ty, you are safe."],[2156,2210,"Which means"],[2210,2519,"Toni, you are eliminated."],[2898,3098,"Oh my God, Sav's staying."],[3566,3703,"I thought I was safe,"],[3703,3895,"but they called my name,"],[3895,4049,"and they're sending me home."],[4049,4162,"I don't want to go home."],[4162,4325,"I'm having a great time here."],[4325,4433,"And I was trying to find"],[4433,4529,"a connection with someone"],[4529,4675,"but it just wasn't there."],[4675,4792,"I'm not happy about it,"],[4792,4875,"but, hey,"],[4888,4984,"you got to take it in stride"],[4984,5184,"and it's going to go along."],[5509,5659,"I'm so shocked."],[6085,6285,"I genuinely think that Ty"],[6285,6389,"is my soulmate,"],[6389,6473,"and I'm just so happy"],[6473,6631,"he didn't get sent home tonight."],[6631,6710,"I'm still reeling."],[6710,6890,"Holy smokes."],[6890,6969,"I'm here to stay."],[6969,7123,"Savannah is my soulmate."],[7123,7273,"I knew it. Sorry, Toni."],[7724,7824,"My singles."],[7824,8020,"You survived elimination."],[8020,8162,"Giving you one more chance"],[8162,8312,"to find your soulmate."],[8312,8404,"I wish you luck"],[8404,8566,"and I'll see you tomorrow."],[8566,8767,"So for the elimination,"],[8767,8837,"we all decided"],[8837,8958,"to band together"],[8958,9188,"and majority vote Sym off"],[9188,9309,"just to give Julie"],[9309,9451,"the chance with her soulmate"],[9451,9588,"because I am convinced"],[9588,9647,"it's her and Cru."],[9647,9755,"And if it's not,"],[9755,9884,"then I've never been more wrong"],[9884,10030,"about anything in my life."],[10030,10264,"I think Cru is my soulmate."],[10268,10418,"I've explored the other"],[10418,10552,"connections in the house"],[10552,10673,"and they don't come close."],[10673,10760,"I was super attracted"],[10760,10923,"to Jace, he's super hot,"],[10923,10998,"but it's different."],[10998,11065,"Like it's different"],[11065,11252,"when you have something beyond"],[11252,11432,"just chemistry with someone."],[11432,11644,"And I just hope Cru can see that."],[11795,11911,"So this is crucial,"],[11911,12016,"we're here to find the soulmate."],[12020,12124,"So for all I know,"],[12124,12183,"Symantha could"],[12183,12270,"have been my soulmate"],[12270,12383,"and now she's not here."],[12391,12587,"But if it is Julie,"],[12587,12691,"because we're still here,"],[12708,12833,"does that mean we're soulmates?"],[12933,13021,"This shit's tough."]],"88":[[179,212,"That was a"],[212,412,"weird feeling tonight."],[425,592,"Because I actually really did like"],[592,696,"Symantha."],[696,896,"I really liked her calm presence."],[925,1042,"It's weird when she left"],[1042,1142,"and she was gone, like"],[1222,1301,"I missed her."],[1301,1463,"Symantha got sent home."],[1463,1609,"She literally just got here."],[1609,1793,"I had a really good connection with her."],[1793,1922,"It absolutely sucked."],[1922,2043,"It tore my heart out."],[2043,2223,"Nobody saw our conversation"],[2223,2327,"that me and Symantha had."],[2327,2485,"Everybody saw the Julie stuff."],[2485,2594,"There was a lot."],[2594,2736,"Even though you guys kind of fight"],[2736,2823,"I kind of feel like"],[2823,2936,"there's a reason you fight."],[3007,3098,"Like you don't fight with people"],[3098,3207,"you don't really care about."],[3207,3311,"It’s very unfortunate"],[3311,3390,"what happened with Sym,"],[3390,3482,"I wish that didn't happen."],[3482,3603,"And I wish that she didn't go home."],[3603,3832,"But hearing Cru talk about Sym,"],[3845,3945,"I can see the softness"],[3945,4037,"in his eyes and his heart."],[4037,4237,"I think he really does like Julie a lot,"],[4237,4379,"but I think that's maybe"],[4379,4491,"because he's a bit more"],[4491,4637,"used to the chaos in his life, and that's"],[4637,4808,"why it's a comfort thing for him."],[4808,4967,"When I truly think someone like Sym,"],[4967,5055,"who really showed him"],[5055,5142,"those kind of values"],[5142,5234,"and that calmness that"],[5234,5317,"he could see in life,"],[5317,5459,"I think that was something"],[5459,5588,"that really blew his mind."],[5588,5634,"Were you guys"],[5634,5755,"persuaded by your ladies,"],[5755,5885,"or was it an honest pick?"],[5922,6035,"No no no, no, for me"],[6035,6106,"it was an honest pick"],[6106,6272,"because I truly think Julie is your pick."],[6272,6352,"That's why."],[6352,6485,"Me and Symantha,"],[6485,6710,"I think we just, I don't know."],[6740,6865,"I think she could be my soulmate."],[6865,6923,"And now"],[7023,7115,"she's gone."],[7115,7307,"They say as quick as you get it,"],[7307,7369,"and so fast"],[7369,7457,"you lose it."],[7457,7540,"Yeah."],[7540,7599,"Yeah."],[7599,7720,"And that's what just happened"],[7720,7799,"with Symantha."],[7799,7845,"I don't know."],[7845,7895,"I need to have"],[7895,8033,"some conversation with Julie,"],[8033,8233,"and I'm just going to sleep on it tonight."],[8270,8521,"Now I'm in a pickle because Julie said,"],[8537,8683,"if you don't pick me right now,"],[8683,8808,"and then Symantha goes home"],[8808,8938,"and you pick me by default,"],[8938,9063,"I'm not going to do that."],[9063,9221,"So you better choose wisely."],[9221,9359,"And that's exactly what happened."],[9359,9467,"She predicted it"],[9467,9576,"or she created it."],[9580,9768,"I don't know what happened."],[9768,9972,"I need to go talk to the girls because"],[9980,10097,"I need some answers."]],"89":[[41,179,"Symantha's gone."],[179,291,"I'm numbed out."],[291,429,"I've been through too much."],[429,592,"Like, put me out coach."],[592,709,"I don't wanna be in the game right now."],[709,775,"This sucks."],[775,913,"And I think the game's over."],[913,1084,"It's only half time."],[1134,1334,"Hello."],[1576,1701,"Question for you ladies."],[1701,1901,"Who'd you guys vote for?"],[1901,1968,"You first."],[1968,2047,"Who do you think?"],[2047,2131,"We all voted the same."],[2131,2306,"We all have each other's backs."],[2306,2427,"We voted for Symantha"],[2427,2498,"because as we"],[2498,2598,"already told you,"],[2598,2727,"she came to all of us"],[2727,2957,"and said she's just here for the show."],[2986,3098,"You're not even her type."],[3098,3178,"She didn't even want to"],[3178,3294,"couple up with you tonight."],[3294,3432,"She only chose you"],[3432,3616,"because I told her to."],[3616,3699,"You're telling me"],[3699,3824,"Symantha never liked me."],[3824,3937,"She didn't care for me."],[3937,4045,"She didn't want to pick me."],[4045,4175,"She was forced to pick me."],[4175,4308,"And now I'm feeling like"],[4308,4433,"a fucking idiot."],[4466,4525,"I feel like"],[4525,4683,"she got girl-ganged up on,"],[4683,4825,"and I didn't get the opportunity"],[4825,4921,"to make my choice."],[4921,5021,"You know, for a fact"],[5021,5163,"I would not tell you"],[5163,5255,"no fucking bullshit,"],[5259,5555,"she said tall, tan, foreign."],[5638,5768,"Everything she described was not,"],[5809,5964,"And what did she say this morning?"],[5964,6031,"Who did she say"],[6031,6081,"she wanted to"],[6081,6185,"couple up with?"],[6185,6256,"Ty."],[6256,6473,"Did I just get played by Symantha?"],[6473,6573,"Am I getting played by"],[6573,6694,"Julie and these girls?"],[6710,6856,"I didn't want to believe it."],[6856,7015,"But when the evidence"],[7015,7082,"is in your face"],[7082,7223,"and you've got four or five"],[7223,7328,"or six eyewitnesses"],[7328,7528,"telling you no, this is the truth,"],[7528,7678,"you think you're going crazy."],[7678,7862,"Your perception is off."],[7862,7937,"I don't think it's off."],[7937,8099,"I think his feelings matter too."],[8099,8191,"And I didn't see a"],[8191,8312,"lot of things apparently."],[8312,8487,"We're literally filling"],[8487,8604,"you in, and you still, like,"],[8604,8700,"won't see the data"],[8700,8804,"that's in front of you."],[8825,9113,"I feel like Cru is being really unfair"],[9113,9184,"when we're, like,"],[9184,9376,"literally in this love war,"],[9376,9501,"one for one for one,"],[9501,9609,"who's going to hurt who worse"],[9609,9718,"so now where do we go?"],[9718,9897,"I don't know what to trust."],[9897,10047,"We have no reason to lie to you."],[10047,10214,"You think we all corroborated"],[10214,10239,"in on the story?"],[10239,10318,"I do trust you."],[10318,10472,"I wish, I would not bullshit you."],[10472,10543,"Mean girls."],[10568,10698,"It was an episode out of Mean Girls."],[10698,10823,"They're attacking me."],[10823,10960,"And keep in mind, this is the girl"],[10960,11161,"that's trying to win me over and think"],[11161,11277,"that I'm her soulmate."],[11277,11419,"And she's just attacking me,"],[11419,11519,"ridiculing me."],[11540,11669,"And apparently this girl"],[11669,11736,"I just put my heart"],[11736,11824,"on the line for"],[11824,11966,"you guys kicked out."],[12007,12141,"I just feel like I'm getting played."]],"90":[[183,321,"I'm going home."],[321,496,"I definitely think I didn't really have"],[496,675,"a chance at finding love"],[675,834,"because I was barely here"],[838,984,"24 hours,"],[984,1126,"and I really didn't get a chance"],[1126,1230,"to get to know anybody"],[1230,1372,"other than just Cru"],[1372,1463,"and some of the girls."],[1480,1593,"It shouldn't have happened."],[1593,1755,"She just got here."],[1755,1885,"I think everybody ganged up"],[1885,2085,"and just kicked her out."],[2202,2314,"Like I actually was not"],[2314,2481,"expecting it to be me."],[2481,2606,"I 100 percent"],[2606,2748,"wanted you to stay."],[2748,2827,"Like real talk."],[2827,3036,"I know, I mean, I wanted to also."],[3036,3190,"I definitely came here"],[3190,3265,"looking for love"],[3265,3403,"and to find my soulmate."],[3403,3520,"Cru and I were really"],[3520,3632,"building a connection."],[3632,3841,"But now that I've been eliminated,"],[3841,3941,"I'm not sure"],[3941,4020,"that we're going to be able"],[4020,4179,"to continue that connection."],[4179,4320,"They're fucking me up."],[4320,4425,"Because I think I'm very smart."],[4425,4608,"They're kind of lowkey mean girls."],[4621,4729,"And they're like, cliquey."],[4729,4800,"Yeah."],[4800,4909,"And full transparency"],[4909,5009,"I think she was too good"],[5009,5217,"of a person and energy to sit here"],[5217,5355,"in the chaos of this house."],[5355,5438,"She was here to find"],[5438,5526,"a soulmate as well."],[5526,5630,"And I think she got the"],[5630,5709,"bad end of the stick."],[5709,5872,"And everybody judged her because"],[5872,5976,"I think they were jealous."],[5976,6181,"Do you like actually somewhat"],[6181,6381,"interested outside of here?"],[6439,6464,"Yeah."],[6681,6848,"Yeah,"],[6848,6948,"Because I think you're"],[6948,7132,"drop dead gorgeous."],[7182,7269,"I don't want to sit here"],[7269,7382,"and, like, love bomb you,"],[7382,7490,"but you are stunning."],[7490,7615,"I think she could be my soulmate."],[7615,7820,"And now she's gone."],[7841,8037,"Hopefully he does find his soulmate."],[8037,8204,"Even if it's not me."],[8204,8316,"And I will be upset."],[8316,8416,"But that's okay."],[8416,8554,"I'll find my soulmate."],[8554,8717,"I do want to kiss you though."],[8717,8917,"Is that okay?"],[9547,9813,"It made me realize, hey, this is serious."],[9813,9922,"I need to crack down."],[9922,10047,"And I need to really figure out"],[10047,10226,"what life could be like"],[10226,10310,"outside of here."],[10314,