 of our tricks?"],[9480,9609,"What the hell was that?"],[9609,9768,"I had a really emotional talk"],[9768,9834,"with the girls"],[9847,9997,"right before Ty got here,"],[10026,10155,"and I never really cry,"],[10155,10289,"but I let some tears loose"],[10289,10452,"because I just felt like I wasn't being"],[10452,10602,"necessarily, like, chosen."],[10623,10764,"Ty gets brought in"],[10764,10923,"and without him even knowing that"],[10923,11115,"that was even a thing, he chose me."],[11144,11265,"And the fact that he came in here"],[11265,11440,"with the confidence to choose"],[11465,11640,"just goes to show that I really do"],[11640,11749,"think that that's my soulmate."],[11891,12066,"I am picking this"],[12066,12228,"person because"],[12441,12512,"I'm scared."],[12512,12608,"I'm terrified."],[12608,12766,"I, I don't even know"],[12766,12867,"if I want this anymore."]],"95":[[25,141,"In order to be a lover, you"],[141,291,"have to be a fighter."],[316,467,"But with that said,"],[542,600,"sometimes"],[600,696,"you kind of have to go"],[696,754,"through the wringer."],[771,950,"You kind of have to hit rock bottom"],[950,1030,"some hard stuff"],[1030,1230,"to really realize what you like"],[1230,1380,"and what you're trying to pursue."],[1430,1647,"And this person has"],[1647,1835,"a lot of similar qualities,"],[1881,1989,"a lot of character"],[1989,2139,"that I love about her."],[2139,2348,"And I think we need to"],[2377,2527,"give this a second chance."],[2594,2744,"If you'll accept this,"],[2752,2902,"I'm down for round two."],[2973,3123,"Round two."],[3390,3461,"It seems like"],[3461,3645,"we've all found our match."],[3645,3799,"Alectra and Josiah"],[3799,4004,"just balance each other out."],[4004,4133,"She is the wild,"],[4133,4262,"he is her calm."],[4262,4546,"The smiles look great on them."],[4546,4683,"We have Jace and Brynn,"],[4683,4867,"they're the safe couple."],[4867,5071,"We have Savannah and Ty,"],[5071,5217,"they are the same people,"],[5217,5317,"d