 the past,"],[3887,4004,"me and Savannah had a little"],[4004,4112,"bit of a connection"],[4112,4208,"but I mean, I really did"],[4208,4391,"want it to be Alectra."],[4963,5096,"Okay, this is weird."],[5096,5146,"Oh my God,"],[5146,5221,"I don't even know what to say"],[5221,5305,"right now."],[5305,5405,"I'm still Team Ty."],[5405,5509,"I'm sorry."],[5509,5668,"I'm Team Alectra."],[5722,5814,"We can still be good friends."],[5814,5968,"-We can be besties. -Yeah."],[5968,6118,"Bring it in."],[6139,6260,"This is weird."],[6260,6368,"You know, we shook hands"],[6368,6406,"we hugged."],[6406,6502,"Had a little cute hug."],[6502,6631,"I mean, I guess if it wasn't Alectra,"],[6631,6840,"Savannah was my match."],[6840,6919,"Best friends forever."],[6919,7036,"Best friends forever."],[7036,7090,"Besties."],[7152,7265,"Apparently, that's who"],[7265,7465,"I should have been trying to get to know"],[7465,7615,"a little bit more the whole time."],[7615,7745,"I have no regrets."],[7745,7816,"I genuinely"],[7816,7999,"think that Ty is still my soulmate"],[7999,8087,"and I would not have"],[8087,8241,"had it any other way."],[8283,8329,"Even though"],[8329,8454,"Savannah is my soulmate"],[8454,8566,"I still think that"],[8566,8692,"Alectra is my soulmate"],[8692,8787,"at the end of the day."]],"113":[[321,492,"I'm really nervous right now."],[529,713,"I feel like Josiah is my soulmate,"],[734,817,"but I don't know"],[817,934,"what the experts think."],[988,1105,"It's got to be Josiah."],[1105,1255,"Who else could it be?"],[1372,1701,"Alectra, your soulmate is..."],[2957,3144,"Please tell me this is a prank."],[3144,3278,"Toni?"],[3278,3386,"Hey."],[3636,3795,"Sorry we voted you off."],[3841,3991,"Very surprised."],[4054,4187,"We didn't even have a connection."],[4187,4216,"I'm like,"],[4216,4391,"what is actually going on?"],[4391,4529,"Tell me y'all lying right now."],[4529,4633,"Tell me y'all are playing a prank."],[4633,4804,"Tell me you're playing a prank."],[4804,4900,"I did say it once."],[4900,5042,"I was like, maybe"],[5042,5309,"like he's funny, but I don't."],[5309,5442,"I didn't think he was cute."],[5442,5538,"And I didn't like being"],[5538,5638,"touched by him."],[5638,5784,"Like, how does that make sense at all?"],[5784,5893,"If he was my connection"],[5893,6001,"we would have..."],[6001,6206,"it's just... the math isn't mathing."],[6206,6364,"This is not making any sense to me."],[6456,6539,"My soulmate is"],[6539,6706,"Josiah, and I'm very shocked"],[6706,6940,"and surprised that I got Toni."],[6986,7094,"Now you got me fucked up."],[7094,7340,"We done. Thank you though."],[7982,8124,"I believe Cru"],[8124,8266,"is my soulmate."],[8366,8591,"I actually don't care what it says"],[8591,8750,"who my soulmate is on paper"],[8750,8942,"because a soulmate is"],[8942,9063,"beyond what's on paper."],[9180,9263,"The connection is"],[9263,9384,"beyond what's on paper."]],"114":[[175,346,"There's truly no"],[346,496,"doubt in my mind"],[496,688,"that Cru is my soulmate."],[784,913,"Julie."],[1076,1217,"Your soulmate is..."],[1468,1639,"No way."],[1714,1856,"What are you doing here?"],[1889,2035,"What are you doing here?"],[2035,2118,"I don't know, soulmate,"],[2118,2152,"you tell me."],[2152,2285,"How did you get here?"],[2285,2406,"What?"],[2406,2477,"Ty."],[2477,2573,"It's Ty."],[2573,2686,"I am hallucinating."],[2686,2777,"Dissociating."],[2777,2911,"I have had a psychotic break"],[2911,3057,"because in no universe"],[3057,3236,"is anyone besides Cru supposed to be"],[3236,3332,"standing in front of me."],[3332,3382,"What do you mean"],[3382,3520,"it's Ty? Ty?"],[3561,3653,"Ty?!"],[3728,3983,"I was not expecting this, hi."],[3983,4049,"Hello."],[4049,4204,"I told Cru that"],[4204,4279,"out of all the girls"],[4279,4450,"I talked to, it's definitely not Julie."],[4450,4533,"She's the last person"],[4533,4633,"that would be my soulmate."],[4633,4783,"Oh, my God, I'm"],[4808,4967,"fucked up in the head."],[5063,5105,"Hey, I guess"],[5105,5255,"that means me too."],[5284,5405,"Yeah, you are too."],[5405,5505,"If I'm your soul mate."],[5505,5584,"You're fucked up in the head."],[5584,5709,"We're fucked up, huh?"],[5709,5839,"I really thought"],[5839,5985,"it was going to be Savannah."],[5985,6051,"You know, we've,"],[6051,6156,"we clicked so fast."],[6156,6252,"I feel like we clicked faster"],[6252,6368,"than all the other couples."],[6368,6414,"Truly."],[6414,6569,"I don't even know what to think."],[6569,6719,"Like, now I'm, like, kind of"],[6756,6902,"Maybe it makes a little"],[6902,7011,"bit, like, now I'm kind of."],[7011,7073,"I'm trying."],[7073,7178,"I'm trying to go back"],[7178,7240,"and think about it too."],[7240,7407,"It shocked me when it wasn't Savannah."],[7407,7549,"I wish it would have been."],[7549,7661,"I believe"],[7661,7853,"that Savannah is my soulmate."],[7853,7978,"Cru is it for me."],[7978,8220,"I felt more butterflies"],[8220,8466,"electricity running through my body"],[8466,8692,"when Cru kissed me on the forehead"],[8692,8817,"than I ever did"],[8817,9075,"putting my tongue inside Ty's mouth."],[9167,9267,"I don't know where this leaves me,"],[9267,9467,"but like for me,"],[9467,9622,"my soulmate's Cru."],[10043,10243,"I could not be more"],[10243,10414,"anxious, more nervous."],[10414,10564,"I've been split in here."],[10564,10764,"I've liked both of these girls,"],[10789,10902,"had so much in common"],[10902,11052,"in different ways."],[11115,11252,"Cru."],[11286,11461,"Your soulmate is..."]],"115":[[254,433,"Oh shit."],[654,771,"No way."],[1138,1301,"I turn around."],[1301,1409,"I got fucking scared."],[1409,1534,"There's a friggin' blow up doll."],[1534,1714,"I was expecting Julie to be there"],[1714,1885,"and we were going to kiss"],[1885,1972,"and be romantic"],[1972,2043,"and I'm, like, all right."],[2043,2177,"She is my soulmate, it worked"],[2177,2369,"like, all the fighting paid off."],[2419,2494,"Wow."],[2573,2731,"I guess that's my answer, right?"],[2731,2852,"I wanted more time."],[2852,2961,"Symantha from day one"],[2961,3119,"the second she walked in..."],[3119,3278,"my feelings never changed for her."],[3278,3465,"I wanted her to be my soulmate"],[3465,3657,"and I guess I finally"],[3657,3766,"get something that I want"],[3766,3891,"after this whole experience."],[3891,4008,"Deep down in my heart"],[4008,4187,"I do think it is Symantha."],[4245,4391,"See, I was right,"],[4391,4512,"I was right."],[4571,4721,"I think you came here to save me"],[4721,4896,"from what I've been dealing with."],[4896,5100,"Also: girl gang"],[5100,5226,"mean girls"],[5226,5430,"Savannah, Alectra...."],[5513,5647,"What the fuck?"],[5693,5784,"You guys lied to me."],[5784,5939,"Lied straight to my face."],[5939,6022,"They tried to"],[6022,6189,"convince me that you were lying"],[6189,6268,"over and over"],[6268,6402,"and it literally messed me up"],[6402,6481,"on the inside because"],[6481,6610,"I didn't believe any of them."],[6610,6806,"This is reassurance for me"],[6806,6956,"and I needed this clarity."],[7294,7415,"Knowing that Symantha"],[7415,7578,"is my soulmate now, it"],[7578,7741,"flips the whole thing upside down"],[7741,7949,"like I think I was being hopeful"],[7949,8058,"I think I was ignoring all"],[8058,8128,"the red flags"],[8128,8304,"and all these repeating patterns."],[8304,8366,"I was right,"],[8366,8487,"Symantha is the soulmate"],[8487,8566,"and I knew that"],[8566,8725,"and guess who got in the way of me"],[8725,8846,"finding my soulmate"],[8846,8983,"and winning the cash prize?"],[9046,9125,"Julie."],[9125,9263,"She set it all up."],[9321,9413,"Is this real?"],[9413,9501,"Do I get to keep her,"],[9501,9588,"or are you just going to"],[9617,9722,"take it away from me again?"],[9722,9763,"-Yes."],[10381,10481,"Which leaves..."],[10552,10689,"our final couple."]],"116":[[408,517,"I do feel like I'm really"],[517,679,"feeling Jace at this moment."],[679,825,"I'm here for a genuine connection"],[825,925,"and I'm feeling it"],[925,1076,"and that's what I'm going to follow."],[1213,1343,"I'm hoping to find a partner who"],[1343,1484,"definitely knows what she wants."],[1484,1668,"Mature, emotionally sound..."],[1668,1768,"Someone I can really"],[1768,1847,"build a life with."],[1847,1985,"Someone who's ready to settle down"],[1985,2102,"and have kids and a family"],[2102,2139,"because that's"],[2139,2256,"a lifelong dream of mine."],[2256,2460,"And I definitely hope that's Brynn."],[2552,2681,"And our final secret"],[2681,2831,"soulmates are"],[3182,3353,"Brynn and Jace."],[3353,3478,"Who knew?"],[3724,3820,"Glad it was you."],[3933,4062,"You surprised?"],[4062,4237,"No because I knew, I knew it."],[4237,4371,"I knew it from the start."],[4371,4517,"We turn around and"],[4517,4688,"lo and behold, it's Brynn."],[4688,4788,"I knew it from day one."],[4788,4859,"I had the hunch."],[4859,4950,"I had the feeling."],[4950,5050,"We've seen it through."],[5080,5159,"We did it."],[5230,5472,"Brynn and Jace are soulmates."],[5518,5643,"Congratulations you guys."],[5680,5826,"You are the only couple"],[5826,5943,"to have guessed correctly."],[5943,6114,"That means together"],[6114,6243,"you'll be leaving the mansion"],[6243,6377,"with the cash prize."],[6377,6523,"But most importantly"],[6523,6702,"you found love."],[6702,6923,"Love."],[6923,7115,"That's all that matters."],[7253,7349,"For Jace and I,"],[7349,7444,"I do feel like a large"],[7444,7570,"part of our connection has"],[7570,7741,"happened outside of the challenges."],[7741,7807,"You know, I don't think"],[7807,7932,"that you need to be the people"],[7932,8028,"who are touching each other"],[8028,8083,"all the time"],[8083,8241,"or getting into arguments"],[8241,8362,"to prove that, you know, there's"],[8362,8450,"some sort of connection"],[8450,8558,"or emotions there."],[8558,8671,"There's more to our connection"],[8671,8729,"than just"],[8729,8888,"what everybody is seeing."],[8988,9125,"Brynn and Jace,"],[9125,9280,"you were the only two to have"],[9280,9438,"guessed your soulmates correctly."],[9467,9576,"How do you feel?"],[9576,9655,"How do I feel about"],[9655,9818,"finding my soulmate here?"],[9818,9939,"I mean, ecstatic, really."],[9939,10005,"Look at her."],[10005,10135,"It couldn't have gone any better."],[10135,10243,"You know, I came on the show,"],[10243,10310,"didn't have the"],[10310,10406,"highest expectations"],[10406,10564,"but I did it with an open mind."],[10564,10806,"And the dice rolled in my favor and"],[10860,10935,"landed Brynn."],[11006,11140,"Of course, I hoped when I was"],[11140,11215,"going to turn around"],[11215,11298,"it was going to be Jace."],[11298,11386,"He probably could tell by the amount"],[11386,11599,"of hairspray that it was me, but..."],[11599,11753,"We knew."],[11945,12045,"I do like you,"],[12045,12203,"and I'm glad we got to meet"],[12203,12320,"and can't wait to see"],[12320,12408,"what comes next."]],"117":[[304,412,"The week is over"],[412,583,"and our singles' secrets and"],[583,763,"soulmates have been revealed."],[925,1046,"So what's next for"],[1046,1180,"our couples after they"],[1180,1305,"leave the mansion?"],[1459,1551,"I got to say that"],[1551,1651,"this has been a week"],[1651,1743,"that I'll never forget,"],[1743,1872,"and it's been one of the best times ever"],[1872,1981,"and I feel like I really made"],[1981,2052,"some friends here."],[2052,2243,"At first I was a little skeptical,"],[2268,2448,"but the parallels are there."],[2469,2560,"It's actually crazy."],[2560,2719,"We have so much in common."],[2719,2857,"He is so cute."],[2857,2969,"I genuinely think that"],[2969,3211,"this is my soulmate."],[3211,3324,"Outside of here, Savannah and I"],[3324,3420,"will definitely go on a date."],[3440,3524,"I definitely think that"],[3524,3603,"we'll have a great date."],[3645,3803,"And I think that we'll honestly,"],[3803,3912,"we'll bond even more"],[3912,4004,"from this experience."],[4029,4212,"Savannah and Ty"],[4212,4354,"felt they had met their soulmates"],[4354,4475,"while at the mansion"],[4475,4654,"and they even spent time together"],[4654,4875,"in Los Angeles, but ultimately"],[4875,5017,"living across the country"],[5017,5117,"from one another"],[5117,5209,"prevented them"],[5209,5376,"from taking their relationship"],[5376,5492,"any further."],[5534,5651,"Me and Josiah really"],[5651,5801,"are the true soulmates."],[5801,5847,"I don't know"],[5847,5989,"y'all math wasn't mathin'"],[5989,6135,"and you need to go back to school."],[6135,6277,"Me and Alectra, we're still going to"],[6277,6352,"see each other"],[6352,6531,"we're still going to see where it goes."],[6552,6702,"I think the future's bright for us."],[6710,6831,"I'm going to go out there"],[6831,6956,"to Florida and we are"],[6956,7098,"going to go to Disney World."],[7098,7186,"We're really going to try"],[7186,7244,"to make this work"],[7244,7344,"and see where this goes."],[7382,7503,"Alectra and Josiah"],[7503,7632,"never made it to Disney World"],[7632,7782,"together but they both felt"],[7782,7853,"they made a real"],[7853,8008,"connection and remained friends."],[8028,8141,"Both are still single."],[8254,8395,"I think Symantha"],[8395,8558,"100 percent could be"],[8558,8625,"someone that"],[8625,8762,"I could start a family with"],[8762,8942,"and be a good stepmother"],[8942,9017,"to my kids."],[9017,9242,"She's so sweet, so sincere,"],[9242,9384,"and that is exactly what I need"],[9384,9438,"in a woman."],[9438,9601,"That's what I came out here to find."],[9601,9751,"That's what I've been looking for"],[9751,9930,"and guess what got in the way of me"],[9930,10035,"finding my soulmate"],[10035,10193,"and winning the cash prize?"],[10193,10272,"Julie."],[10272,10410,"I feel like I left here"],[10410,10527,"kind of a loser."],[10527,10656,"I didn't guess my soulmate."],[10656,10756,"I didn't win the money."],[10785,10935,"The person that I wanted"],[10935,11094,"is soulmates with someone"],[11094,11182,"who I broke up"],[11182,11319,"I broke them up essentially."],[11344,11498,"So where does that leave me?"],[11603,11724,"Shortly after the show"],[11724,11874,"Julie moved to Utah"],[11874,12045,"to quadruple down with Cru."],[12045,12145,"While she was away,"],[12145,12274,"a tragic accident"],[12274,12387,"occurred resulting in"],[12387,12566,"the death of her beloved dog"],[12566,12700,"and it's Julie's opinion"],[12721,12912,"Cru is partially to blame."],[12950,13100,"They have since broken up."],[13204,13275,"Cru and Symantha"],[13275,13392,"talk all the time"],[13392,13551,"and he is planning to visit her"],[13551,13634,"in Austin."],[13717,13826,"You know, like we've done here,"],[13826,13884,"we're just going to keep"],[13884,14018,"taking things day by day"],[14018,14114,"and see where it goes."],[14114,14172,"I don't know if I have"],[14172,14289,"the accent for Brooklyn."],[14289,14443,"That's probably true."],[14460,14572,"I have been a Georgia girl once."],[14572,14706,"I can be a Georgia girl again."],[14706,14789,"There we go."],[14823,14935,"My neck of the woods."],[14981,15223,"Brynn and Jace are no longer together."],[15223,15377,"Both only have good things to say"],[15377,15457,"about one another"],[15457,15523,"and they credit"],[15523,15623,"Secrets and Soulmates"],[15623,15749,"with giving them the courage"],[15749,15824,"to date again"],[15824,15890,"and the hope"],[15890,16024,"that they'll find love."],[16061,16216,"How's the cast doing now?"],[16216,16341,"And how do they feel about what"],[16341,16524,"happened after they left the show?"],[16558,16670,"Big secrets!"],[16670,16775,"Big drama!"],[16808,16896,"And maybe?"],[16912,17050,"Another soulmate reveal"],[17050,17192,"when the cast gathers again"],[17192,17371,"for a reunion on ReelTalk."],[17404,17496,"Stay tuned!"]]}